conference_name_desc_form=Dear Manager,<br>Brussels College (BIBT) is a new private higher education institution in Brussels, Belgium, dedicated to developing attractive Bachelor degree pathways for international graduates.<br>We believe Belgium offers compelling advantages, including more affordable tuition and living costs (approx. one-third of the UK and one fourth of the US), alongside excellent student employment and post-graduation career prospects.<br>To ensure accessibility, we provide an English prep school and a Foundation program even for students without A-Level/IB, with an English prep option also available.<br>This form serves as an initial contact point to gauge your graduates interest in studying in Belgium and their program preferences. Your brief input (approx. 2-3 minutes) will help us tailor potential collaboration opportunities relevant to your school and students.<br>Thank you for considering this opportunity to connect. <br><br><b>Please complete the following sections to share your valuable insights.</b>
